Monday inspo coming your way🤍👙

You may have heard this before but I’m going to share with you anyway! x

Change your “I have to” ➡️ “I get to”

• You don’t HAVE to workout, you GET to.
• You don’t HAVE to eat healthy to feel good, you GET to.
• You don’t HAVE to work hard for what you desire, you GET to.

The saying “you don’t know what you have until it’s gone” has always been true. So take a moment today to be grateful to live this life, to make your own choices and to be happy & healthy. 

Instead of focusing on what you don’t have, focus on what you do have. There’s always going to be more materialistic things you’ll want, more experiences you’ll want to live & more destinations you’ll want to visit. 

Just know that the more you give, the more you will get in return. 

HAPPY MONDAY!! x
